Subject: Netwrix Auditor Scheduled Jobs not running
Description: Looks like the reports in StealthAudit are no longer refreshing. The console hasn't updated since 3/25. I tried to remote into the servers but can no longer reach them. I haven't connected since they migrated so I'm assuming that is why.
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c: Account was somehow wrongly entered in the schedule credentials.
What_We_Know__c: Conatct change the credential in the scheduled task with the same service account as before and it started running.
Solution_Comment__c: Contact noted “I change the credential in the scheduled task with the same service account as before and it started running.”
